- - - ---------------------------------------------------------------------

This advisory contains the correct values for VERSIONS AFFECTED and 
FIXED VERSION

SOLUTION

It is recommended that all Gentoo Linux users who are running
net-www/horde upgrade to horde-2.2.4_rc2 as follows:

emerge sync
emerge horde
emerge clean

